'"},{"content":"Place water into mixing bowl. Place Varoma dish into position, then place zucchini and carrots into it. Secure Varoma lid and steam <b>6-8 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until tender. Transfer zucchini and carrots into a large bowl."},{"content":"Add sugar snap peas to large bowl with other vegetables and toss to combine. Transfer into serving bowls and top with reserved pesto. Garnish with Parmesan cheese and pepper before serving."}],"hintsAndTricks":["We recommend using a vegetable peeler with a spiral or 'spaghetti' attachment to peel zucchini and carrot. Alternatively, peel vegetables and cut into very thin strips."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","45m","4 portions"]}